message:
Dedicated Law Enforcement and Prosecutors work tirelessly to obtain justice for individuals who have been victimized by human traffickers. 
"As this case demonstrates, sex trafficking is a cruel and callous business, in which violence and threats are often used to control victims. It’s our duty to hold traffickers such as Mr. Lewis accountable for the horrendous acts they commit.“
#makingadifference

data.description: Through the efforts of the San Bernardino County Human Trafficking Task Force and the district attorney’s office, Brandon Edward Lewis (Age 35 of Highland) will be spending 73 years in prison for human trafficking, pimping, and other crimes.
data.title: Teen Girls Rescued, Violent Human Trafficker Gets Lengthy Prison Sentence - San Bernardino County District Attorney
